Methods

normalizeConfig()

Connection-level options; connect_retry: Should try to re-establish a connection in case of connection loss. connect_retry_interval_sec: Attempt delay to reopen websocket connection after detecting its loss queue_capacity: Request queue size. When max is reached older requests are dropped first_message_id: The initial value of the correlation id; (override for debugging/testing only)
